<i>Narrator: Previously on TURN:
Washington's Spies.</i>

2
00:00:02,412 --> 00:00:04,922
This was torn from the loyal
exchequer's balance ledger.

3
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:06,931
This seal must reach Versailles.

4
00:00:07,032 --> 00:00:09,113
