6
00:00:11,225 --> 00:00:15,447
Fierce word to King George that
I would kill who ever saw this.

7
00:00:15,548 --> 00:00:16,785
You wanted to be caught.

8
00:00:16,886 --> 00:00:18,890
Male voice: You haven't learned a thing.

9
00:00:19,058 --> 00:00:22,170
If we get Hewlett back from Setauket
he can release Abe from prison.

10
00:00:22,271 --> 00:00:23,480
I'll finish Hewlett.

11
00:00:23,581 --> 00:00:24,347
Happy New Year major.

